snippet.title: Super Rare Mixtape Vol. 3 📼 36 game montage!
snippet.description:
Super Rare Mixtape Vol. 3 - on sale May 26th, 6pm BST at www.superraregames.com 📼

Here's a quick look at all the 30 games + 6 demos included on the Mixtape, including the cult classic Dink Smallwood HD. 

The Mixtape comes in a collectible box with a full-colour manual and a USB shaped like a tape cassette, with a fully custom games launcher on for easy use! You'll also find bonus features like concept art galleries + developer audio commentaries, helping physically preserve these indie games forever. ♥

Thanks for helping support Ryan's personal passion project! We'd love to make more volumes but we'll need your help and support to do so. 💪
